txt.en: 'The old dwarf ruins of Shathur-munzu have been quiet for years and years, but no longer. Wargs dwell there now, and they pose a very real threat to those travelling on the road, and to those who herd sheep in Duskenvale. Make war upon the wargs, and make this land safe from them once again.'
Wargs have become a threat to the good folk of the Vales of Anduin, and must be defeated.
The Beorning Ragnild is concerned about the threat posed by the wargs of Duskenvale.
